1
00:00:11,760 --> 00:00:16,320
[Hanzhou City; 2002]

2
00:00:34,750 --> 00:00:35,430
Don't move.

3
00:00:40,030 --> 00:00:40,640
Mentor,

4
00:00:40,840 --> 00:00:41,780
is your face okay?

5
00:00:41,780 --> 00:00:42,540
It's fine.

6
00:00:42,640 --> 00:00:43,640
Mentor!

7
00:00:44,640 --> 00:00:45,820
Senior Feng!

8
00:00:45,990 --> 00:00:47,050
-Get up.
-Let’s go.

9
00:00:47,840 --> 00:00:48,950
-Help!
-Let’s go.

10
00:00:51,320 --> 00:00:52,170
Mentor!

11
00:00:52,440 --> 00:00:53,070
Mentor!

12
00:00:53,530 --> 00:00:55,720
How did you end up hanging there?
Come over here.

13
00:00:55,720 --> 00:00:56,320
Squat here.

14
00:00:56,320 --> 00:00:57,180
What happened?

15
00:00:58,840 --> 00:00:59,660
Sir,

16
00:01:00,070 --> 00:01:02,600
there was a small accident
during the arrest.

17
00:01:02,960 --> 00:01:04,420
You're really something.

18
00:01:05,040 --> 00:01:05,760
Come on.

19
00:01:05,780 --> 00:01:07,780
Take off your clothes and jump down.

20
00:01:07,920 --> 00:01:09,560
I can't move my arms now.

21
00:01:09,710 --> 00:01:10,950
I'll help you down.

22
00:01:10,950 --> 00:01:12,010
-Come on.
-Come on.

23
00:01:12,900 --> 00:01:13,740
Come on.

24
00:01:13,870 --> 00:01:15,050
Come on, make an effort.

25
00:01:15,050 --> 00:01:15,720
Come on.

26
00:01:15,840 --> 00:01:17,300
Come on. Give him support.

27
00:01:17,320 --> 00:01:18,580
Take off your clothes.

28
00:01:19,200 --> 00:01:20,130
Can you reach it?

29
00:01:22,570 --> 00:01:23,830
Take off your clothes!

30
00:01:24,120 --> 00:01:24,970
Idiot.

31
00:01:27,760 --> 00:01:28,690
Support me a bit.

32
00:01:35,120 --> 00:01:37,550
You're truly a genius.

33
00:01:37,990 --> 00:01:39,320
How can you be so stupid?

34
00:01:40,150 --> 00:01:42,070
Mentor, what happened to your face?

35
00:01:42,070 --> 00:01:43,330
This guy scratched me.

36
00:01:44,979 --> 00:01:47,030
Like mentor, like student.

37
00:01:47,640 --> 00:01:49,039
Who are you talking about?

38
00:01:49,039 --> 00:01:50,500
You didn't see it just now.

39
00:01:50,590 --> 00:01:52,310
I pinned him down in one swift move.

40
00:01:52,310 --> 00:01:53,770
Right, very efficiently.

41
00:01:54,789 --> 00:01:55,890
I'll deal with you later.

42
00:01:55,890 --> 00:01:57,220
Let’s go. Take him back.

43
00:01:57,229 --> 00:01:58,289
-Let’s go.
-Get up.

44
00:03:09,540 --> 00:03:19,930
[The Punishment]

45
00:03:20,120 --> 00:03:20,370
[Punish those who commit crimes
and make mistakes]

46
00:03:20,370 --> 00:03:20,620
[so as to discipline them,]

47
00:03:20,620 --> 00:03:21,130
[and execute those
who violate the prohibitions]

48
00:03:21,130 --> 00:03:22,140
[so as to terrify would-be violators.]

49
00:03:22,170 --> 00:03:23,920
[Guanzi – On Laws and Standards]

50
00:03:24,550 --> 00:03:27,500
[Episode 22]

51
00:03:28,050 --> 00:03:29,040
What do you think?

52
00:03:29,040 --> 00:03:30,210
Are you interested in going

53
00:03:30,210 --> 00:03:31,610
to gain some experience?

54
00:03:31,620 --> 00:03:33,420
Director Chu, your intention is

55
00:03:33,710 --> 00:03:35,900
to have me work in a new department?

56
00:03:36,200 --> 00:03:36,790
Yes.

57
00:03:37,360 --> 00:03:38,420
Once you're there,

58
00:03:38,680 --> 00:03:39,630
after a few years of experience,

59
00:03:39,630 --> 00:03:42,480
I'll find a way to transfer you
to the provincial department.

60
00:03:42,480 --> 00:03:45,940
Our Criminal Investigation Division
needs young people now.

61
00:03:46,590 --> 00:03:47,790
You're a perfect fit.

62
00:03:51,400 --> 00:03:52,200
Director Chu.

63
00:03:52,480 --> 00:03:54,590
Is this Director Ye's idea?

64
00:03:56,810 --> 00:03:58,810
Director Yan recommended you to me.

65
00:03:59,460 --> 00:04:01,760
He's very optimistic
about your future development.

66
00:04:01,760 --> 00:04:02,540
Of course,

67
00:04:02,630 --> 00:04:03,750
Ye is your mentor,

68
00:04:03,750 --> 00:04:05,120
so he'll naturally be happy

69
00:04:05,120 --> 00:04:06,030
to see you move up,

70
00:04:06,030 --> 00:04:06,710
right?

71
00:04:07,110 --> 00:04:07,830
Yes.

72
00:04:11,190 --> 00:04:11,990
Director Chu.

73
00:04:12,060 --> 00:04:12,190
[Hanzhou Public Security Bureau]

74
00:04:12,190 --> 00:04:13,310
Our bureau

75
00:04:13,840 --> 00:04:15,840
has been focusing on several cases

76
00:04:16,630 --> 00:04:18,890
and we've just made some breakthroughs.

77
00:04:18,950 --> 00:04:20,149
If I leave now,

78
00:04:21,470 --> 00:04:23,070
it might not be appropriate.

79
00:04:24,380 --> 00:04:25,190
Qin Feng,

80
00:04:25,430 --> 00:04:26,190
look,

81
00:04:26,800 --> 00:04:28,310
moving from section chief
to deputy director

82
00:04:28,310 --> 00:04:30,960
is a crucial turning point in your career.

83
00:04:31,370 --> 00:04:32,680
Once you cross this threshold,

84
00:04:32,680 --> 00:04:35,480
many important responsibilities
will await you.

85
00:04:37,520 --> 00:04:38,650
Please reconsider.

86
00:04:40,060 --> 00:04:40,860
Director Chu.

87
00:04:42,810 --> 00:04:44,010
The Municipal Bureau

88
00:04:44,510 --> 00:04:45,270
has been working on several cases

89
00:04:45,270 --> 00:04:46,480
for many years now.

90
00:04:47,010 --> 00:04:49,340
I really don't want
to leave at this point.

91
00:04:49,380 --> 00:04:50,020
All right.

92
00:04:50,750 --> 00:04:51,920
Your future

93
00:04:52,070 --> 00:04:53,070
is your choice.

94
00:04:53,620 --> 00:04:54,420
I respect you.

95
00:04:56,190 --> 00:04:58,240
Thank you for understanding, Director Chu.

96
00:04:58,240 --> 00:04:58,800
Alright.

97
00:04:59,159 --> 00:05:00,540
We have plenty of time ahead.

98
00:05:00,540 --> 00:05:01,990
Just focus on solving your current cases.

99
00:05:01,990 --> 00:05:02,630
I will.

100
00:05:02,650 --> 00:05:03,280
Good.

101
00:05:05,970 --> 00:05:08,100
How did your talk with Director Chu go?

102
00:05:08,190 --> 00:05:08,990
Did you agree?

103
00:05:09,530 --> 00:05:10,260
No, I didn't.

104
00:05:10,890 --> 00:05:11,620
Director Ye,

105
00:05:12,360 --> 00:05:14,090
I'm counting on you from now on.

106
00:05:16,760 --> 00:05:18,890
You're putting the pressure on me now.

107
00:05:20,720 --> 00:05:22,330
You called me here

108
00:05:23,120 --> 00:05:24,590
to investigate this case.

109
00:05:24,800 --> 00:05:26,390
Now the case isn't solved.

110
00:05:26,750 --> 00:05:28,550
Nothing has been accomplished.

111
00:05:28,720 --> 00:05:29,920
How can I leave?

112
00:05:30,440 --> 00:05:31,480
You rascal,

113
00:05:31,500 --> 00:05:32,870
you're pushing me.

114
00:05:36,120 --> 00:05:37,470
As police officers,

115
00:05:37,500 --> 00:05:40,230
we all have a few cases
in our lives we can't solve.

116
00:05:40,520 --> 00:05:41,320
But

117
00:05:42,450 --> 00:05:43,420
I don't want

118
00:05:43,480 --> 00:05:45,740
you to spend your whole life on this.

119
00:05:46,680 --> 00:05:48,260
Mai has left the force,

120
00:05:48,540 --> 00:05:49,870
and Xiaoyue is gone.

121
00:05:51,370 --> 00:05:52,280
To be honest,

122
00:05:52,700 --> 00:05:54,409
I hope you and Zeng Xu

123
00:05:55,300 --> 00:05:57,230
can have good career development.

124
00:05:58,730 --> 00:06:00,060
This is the job we do.

125
00:06:00,120 --> 00:06:01,950
What's the difference
which case I investigate?

126
00:06:01,950 --> 00:06:02,600
It's fine.

127
00:06:03,190 --> 00:06:05,280
So you've made up your mind.

128
00:06:07,800 --> 00:06:08,600
However,

129
00:06:09,200 --> 00:06:11,300
I find this situation suspicious.

130
00:06:11,550 --> 00:06:13,280
You just got a lead on Qiao Defu,

131
00:06:13,360 --> 00:06:16,030
and suddenly someone wants
to transfer you away.

132
00:06:16,030 --> 00:06:19,890
It feels like they're trying to draw
the tiger away from the mountain.

133
00:06:20,580 --> 00:06:22,650
[Hanzhou Public Security Bureau]

134
00:06:22,650 --> 00:06:23,280
Come in.

135
00:06:25,900 --> 00:06:28,510
-Hanzhang. Hanzhang.
-Sister.

136
00:06:28,560 --> 00:06:29,720
What's going on, Sister?

137
00:06:29,720 --> 00:06:32,240
I raised you since you were little.

138
00:06:32,240 --> 00:06:34,510
-I never begged you, right?
-Yes.

139
00:06:34,600 --> 00:06:37,510
This time I'm begging you to help me.

140
00:06:37,510 --> 00:06:38,520
Get up first.

141
00:06:38,550 --> 00:06:39,680
Get up first. Come on.

142
00:06:39,680 --> 00:06:41,870
Please help me.

143
00:06:42,720 --> 00:06:43,040
Keep your voice down.

144
00:06:43,040 --> 00:06:43,680
Okay.

145
00:06:43,680 --> 00:06:44,940
Tell me what happened.

146
00:06:45,510 --> 00:06:47,110
Your little nephew...

147
00:06:47,480 --> 00:06:48,640
Was drunk driving

148
00:06:48,750 --> 00:06:49,950
and hit someone.

149
00:06:49,950 --> 00:06:53,070
The victim is seriously injured
and in the hospital.

150
00:06:53,070 --> 00:06:54,920
What are we going to do?

151
00:06:54,920 --> 00:06:55,800
Dayong?

152
00:06:55,800 --> 00:06:57,080
Yes.

153
00:06:57,360 --> 00:06:58,960
That little bastard

154
00:06:59,040 --> 00:07:00,570
is always causing trouble.

155
00:07:01,120 --> 00:07:02,050
Was he detained?

156
00:07:02,160 --> 00:07:02,870
Which brigade?

157
00:07:02,870 --> 00:07:03,630
No detention.

158
00:07:03,630 --> 00:07:04,630
No police report.

159
00:07:05,000 --> 00:07:06,600
They're negotiating, right?

160
00:07:06,600 --> 00:07:07,360
Your second sister

161
00:07:07,360 --> 00:07:09,210
is negotiating with them now.

162
00:07:09,230 --> 00:07:11,370
I still want to settle this privately.

163
00:07:11,390 --> 00:07:13,870
He just got a permanent position.

164
00:07:13,950 --> 00:07:15,780
If he gets arrested...

165
00:07:15,920 --> 00:07:18,510
-His future will be ruined.
-Lower your voice.

166
00:07:18,510 --> 00:07:19,630
I'll keep my voice down.

167
00:07:19,630 --> 00:07:20,510
I'll speak softly.

168
00:07:20,510 --> 00:07:21,800
I'll speak softly.

169
00:07:21,800 --> 00:07:22,510
Hanzhang.

170
00:07:22,720 --> 00:07:23,680
The biggest problem is

171
00:07:23,680 --> 00:07:24,750
somehow they found out

172
00:07:24,750 --> 00:07:26,790
that we are related to you.

173
00:07:27,390 --> 00:07:29,200
They know Dayong is my nephew?

174
00:07:29,310 --> 00:07:30,570
They know everything.

175
00:07:30,870 --> 00:07:33,230
They're demanding one million,
like highway robbery.

176
00:07:33,230 --> 00:07:35,560
If we don't pay,
they'll make a huge scene.

177
00:07:35,700 --> 00:07:36,960
They're extorting us.

178
00:07:37,800 --> 00:07:39,060
Who is the other party?

179
00:07:39,270 --> 00:07:40,510
I don't know.

180
00:07:40,550 --> 00:07:42,510
They're just local thugs.

181
00:07:42,600 --> 00:07:43,480
They're

182
00:07:43,480 --> 00:07:44,510
local punks.

183
00:07:44,510 --> 00:07:45,370
Yes.

184
00:07:45,430 --> 00:07:46,040
I think

185
00:07:46,040 --> 00:07:47,140
you should step in

186
00:07:47,240 --> 00:07:48,310
and talk to them.

187
00:07:48,630 --> 00:07:50,020
If you show up as the Director,

188
00:07:50,020 --> 00:07:50,770
maybe

189
00:07:51,120 --> 00:07:52,120
you can intimidate them.

190
00:07:52,120 --> 00:07:53,860
That's right, Hanzhang.

191
00:07:54,040 --> 00:07:54,720
Brother.

192
00:07:55,150 --> 00:07:56,700
This isn't that simple.

193
00:07:57,680 --> 00:07:58,190
Sister.

194
00:07:58,700 --> 00:08:00,360
I already know what happened.

195
00:08:00,480 --> 00:08:01,350
Don't worry.

196
00:08:01,430 --> 00:08:02,480
I'll figure something out.

197
00:08:02,480 --> 00:08:03,120
Go home first

198
00:08:03,120 --> 00:08:04,000
and try not to worry.

199
00:08:04,000 --> 00:08:04,990
No, no, no.

200
00:08:05,160 --> 00:08:06,060
Hanzhang.

201
00:08:06,360 --> 00:08:09,600
You're the only official
our whole family has ever supported.

202
00:08:09,600 --> 00:08:10,560
If I can't rely on you,

203
00:08:10,560 --> 00:08:11,870
who else can I turn to?

204
00:08:11,870 --> 00:08:13,560
Didn't I say I'd work on it?

205
00:08:13,560 --> 00:08:14,810
Keep your voice down.

206
00:08:15,120 --> 00:08:15,520
You...

207
00:08:15,830 --> 00:08:16,510
Lower your voice.

208
00:08:16,510 --> 00:08:17,600
I'll lower my voice.

209
00:08:17,600 --> 00:08:19,720
You must help me.

210
00:08:19,760 --> 00:08:21,200
Go back first.

211
00:08:22,070 --> 00:08:23,240
Hurry up.

212
00:08:24,430 --> 00:08:25,120
We'll go back and wait for updates.

213
00:08:25,120 --> 00:08:26,020
Okay.

214
00:08:27,000 --> 00:08:28,080
I'll look into it.

215
00:08:28,510 --> 00:08:29,160
Okay.

216
00:08:29,390 --> 00:08:30,040
Okay.

217
00:08:49,720 --> 00:08:50,580
Director Peng.

218
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:54,210
The fact that you thought of me
when your family had trouble

219
00:08:54,210 --> 00:08:56,860
shows you still consider me a friend.

220
00:08:59,810 --> 00:09:01,450
I came to ask you something.

221
00:09:03,390 --> 00:09:04,770
Did you deliberately

222
00:09:06,630 --> 00:09:08,480
set up the accident?

223
00:09:12,120 --> 00:09:12,870
So now

224
00:09:14,740 --> 00:09:16,270
you're here to solve a case?

225
00:09:19,790 --> 00:09:21,240
I think the most urgent matter now

226
00:09:21,240 --> 00:09:23,010
is to save your nephew.

227
00:09:23,840 --> 00:09:24,960
About your nephew's issue,

228
00:09:24,960 --> 00:09:27,090
I can solve it with just one phone call.

229
00:09:27,870 --> 00:09:29,000
I'll call right now.

230
00:09:35,690 --> 00:09:36,520
Biao.

231
00:09:38,350 --> 00:09:40,070
Are you pushing your luck?

232
00:09:41,990 --> 00:09:45,320
After I went back last time, I thought
about it and decided to let it go.

233
00:09:45,320 --> 00:09:47,490
It's all ancient history now.

234
00:09:48,390 --> 00:09:49,450
I can put up with it.

235
00:09:50,120 --> 00:09:52,060
We can each live our own lives in peace.

236
00:09:52,060 --> 00:09:53,530
If you push me like this,

237
00:09:54,850 --> 00:09:57,450
then it will be
mutually assured destruction.

238
00:09:59,360 --> 00:10:01,510
Peng Hanzhang, have you lost your mind?

239
00:10:01,510 --> 00:10:02,080
What?

240
00:10:02,840 --> 00:10:04,980
You think any little thing
that happens in your family

241
00:10:04,980 --> 00:10:06,420
is all my doing?

242
00:10:07,850 --> 00:10:10,000
You're jumping at shadows.

243
00:10:11,960 --> 00:10:13,820
Being a cop has made you paranoid.

244
00:10:15,150 --> 00:10:16,090
Let me tell you.

245
00:10:17,600 --> 00:10:19,080
You should think carefully about

246
00:10:19,080 --> 00:10:20,480
where you came from.

247
00:10:22,000 --> 00:10:23,410
I know about your family.

248
00:10:24,850 --> 00:10:26,250
Your parents died early.

249
00:10:27,750 --> 00:10:30,200
Your eldest sister brought up

250
00:10:30,220 --> 00:10:32,740
all of you the hard way, didn't she?

251
00:10:34,150 --> 00:10:36,150
How did you become Deputy Director?

252
00:10:36,870 --> 00:10:39,330
Your eldest sister
paid for your education!

253
00:10:39,720 --> 00:10:40,380
So what now?

254
00:10:41,340 --> 00:10:42,540
Now she's in trouble.

255
00:10:43,050 --> 00:10:44,580
Her child is in trouble.

256
00:10:44,720 --> 00:10:46,390
Who can she rely on?

257
00:10:47,940 --> 00:10:50,340
You only think about
yourself all day long.

258
00:11:13,990 --> 00:11:14,680
Hanzhang.

259
00:11:17,070 --> 00:11:18,470
I know you're a person

260
00:11:18,830 --> 00:11:20,960
who's honest and clean as an official.

261
00:11:22,190 --> 00:11:25,600
You've never given
or taken a bribe in your life.

262
00:11:29,510 --> 00:11:30,840
After all these decades

263
00:11:31,830 --> 00:11:32,940
of work,

264
00:11:35,510 --> 00:11:37,780
why are you still just a Deputy Director?

265
00:11:40,390 --> 00:11:41,720
I'm quite content.

266
00:11:41,720 --> 00:11:42,980
Well, I'm not content.

267
00:11:44,510 --> 00:11:45,510
Why should you be?

268
00:11:50,030 --> 00:11:50,990
Let me tell you.

269
00:11:51,320 --> 00:11:53,250
It's because you never socialize,

270
00:11:54,020 --> 00:11:55,860
because you don't network.

271
00:11:58,550 --> 00:12:00,080
Only by networking

272
00:12:00,080 --> 00:12:01,810
can people help each other out.

273
00:12:04,390 --> 00:12:05,630
I'm now working closely

274
00:12:05,630 --> 00:12:07,360
with someone called Zhang Xin.

275
00:12:08,270 --> 00:12:09,640
The person above her

276
00:12:09,700 --> 00:12:10,750
has enormous power

277
00:12:10,750 --> 00:12:12,410
and can make anything happen.

278
00:12:14,510 --> 00:12:15,750
Whether you get promoted

279
00:12:15,750 --> 00:12:17,480
from this deputy director post

280
00:12:17,600 --> 00:12:19,280
is just one word from them.

281
00:12:30,090 --> 00:12:30,890
I've decided.

282
00:12:34,150 --> 00:12:37,660
I must connect you
with them

283
00:12:39,560 --> 00:12:41,490
and help you climb another step up.

284
00:12:50,320 --> 00:12:52,740
Regarding rumors about Chengjian Group's
broken capital chain,

285
00:12:52,740 --> 00:12:54,590
Chengjian headquarters responded today,

286
00:12:54,590 --> 00:12:57,190
stating the rumors
are completely unfounded.

287
00:12:57,270 --> 00:12:58,840
Chengjian Group has sufficient funds

288
00:12:58,840 --> 00:13:00,130
and is operating normally...

289
00:13:00,130 --> 00:13:01,930
Isn't that Qiao Defu's company?

