466
00:19:52,660 --> 00:19:53,510
Yes.

467
00:19:56,550 --> 00:19:57,440
Mom.

468
00:19:58,290 --> 00:20:00,550
This incident has a significant impact.

469
00:20:00,720 --> 00:20:02,240
