487
00:20:44,030 --> 00:20:45,070
Assisting with the investigation?

488
00:20:45,070 --> 00:20:45,590
Yes.

489
00:20:45,790 --> 00:20:47,640
What's really going on with Qiao Defu?

490
00:20:47,640 --> 00:20:48,840
We've been deceived.

491
00:20:49,750 --> 00:20:52,070
The money that was meant
for the real estate project

492
00:20:52,070 --> 00:20:54,680
has all been used by Qiao Defu
to fill his own financial holes.

493
00:20:54,680 --> 00:20:55,310
How much?

494
00:20:55,720 --> 00:20:56,750
All the working capital

495
00:20:56,750 --> 00:20:59,350
of the logistics company
and the chicken farm,

496
00:21:00,030 --> 00:21:01,720
