508
00:21:17,030 --> 00:21:18,850
I know, Mom. Don't worry.

509
00:21:19,160 --> 00:21:20,550
I can't speak for my brother.

510
00:21:20,550 --> 00:21:22,210
He has to explain for himself.

511
00:21:22,310 --> 00:21:23,920
You see, I told him long ago

512
00:21:23,920 --> 00:21:27,380
not to get involved with these people,
but he wouldn't listen.

513
00:21:27,590 --> 00:21:28,200
It's okay.

514
00:21:29,200 --> 00:21:30,530
The specific situation

515
00:21:30,720 --> 00:21:31,780
of Chengjian Group

516
00:21:31,830 --> 00:21:34,030
will depend on the findings
of the higher-level investigation.

517
00:21:34,030 --> 00:21:35,680
Whatever evidence we have,

518
00:21:35,820 --> 00:21:36,550
get it ready.

519
00:21:36,590 --> 00:21:38,350
