526
00:21:49,750 --> 00:21:50,440
Ziyi,

527
00:21:51,160 --> 00:21:53,160
about Zhao Village,
please ask Peng

528
00:21:53,400 --> 00:21:54,880
to help calm things down there.

529
00:21:54,880 --> 00:21:55,920
I will.

530
00:21:56,920 --> 00:21:57,780
It's okay, Mom.

531
00:21:58,110 --> 00:21:58,840
Don't worry.

532
00:21:59,070 --> 00:22:00,480
