535
00:22:03,790 --> 00:22:04,920
Alright.

536
00:22:05,000 --> 00:22:06,070
Okay, it's fine.

537
00:22:09,550 --> 00:22:11,150
There's nothing to discuss.

538
00:22:11,400 --> 00:22:12,510
If we take care of He Biao,

539
00:22:12,510 --> 00:22:14,440
