541
00:22:18,240 --> 00:22:18,830
Peng.

542
00:22:20,030 --> 00:22:20,940
Say something!

543
00:22:21,110 --> 00:22:23,200
He's your sister's husband, isn't he?

544
00:22:23,200 --> 00:22:24,600
What do you want me to say?

545
00:22:25,550 --> 00:22:26,790
Don't I want to save him?

546
00:22:26,790 --> 00:22:28,150
The question is how.

547
00:22:28,350 --> 00:22:29,880
Just tell me if you dare or not.

548
00:22:29,880 --> 00:22:31,310
