549
00:22:31,400 --> 00:22:32,530
Don't be impulsive.

550
00:22:33,720 --> 00:22:35,050
Let's think about this.

551
00:22:35,510 --> 00:22:37,550
He Biao has been in Hanzhou
for so many years.

552
00:22:37,550 --> 00:22:38,550
Ma Jin fell,

553
00:22:38,550 --> 00:22:39,480
but they didn't.

554
00:22:39,830 --> 00:22:40,400
Why?

555
00:22:40,750 --> 00:22:41,280
Exactly.

556
00:22:42,720 --> 00:22:44,350
Do you really think He Biao alone

557
00:22:44,350 --> 00:22:45,510
can make the ECID

558
00:22:45,720 --> 00:22:46,790
