560
00:22:47,960 --> 00:22:49,930
I don't care who's backing him.

561
00:22:50,310 --> 00:22:51,510
If they touch my brother,

562
00:22:51,510 --> 00:22:52,640
I'll deal with them.

563
00:22:53,030 --> 00:22:53,830
