564
00:22:54,200 --> 00:22:55,240
If you take care of He Biao,

565
00:22:55,240 --> 00:22:56,590
will your brother be released?

566
00:22:56,590 --> 00:22:58,270
Can we stop thinking
about eliminating people

567
00:22:58,270 --> 00:23:00,130
and focus on solving the problem?

568
00:23:00,640 --> 00:23:02,770
